    "text": "In the spirit of our <#C5T9GPWFL|thinking-together> capitalism thread. I found <https://informal.systems/2020/09/21/informal-owners/|https://informal.systems/2020/09/21/informal-owners/> i think this is an interesting example of how to change the bigger structure- capitalism (this time I spelled it out <@U5STGTB3J> :sweat_smile:  ) by changing smaller structures I.e. companies to cooperatives.",
