        "fallback": "Informal Organizations: Iterating on Cooperative Ownership",
        "text": "Our mission at Informal Systems is not just about distributed systems, it&amp;#39;s also about the organizations that grow along with them. Our vision is an open-source ecosystem of cooperatively owned and governed distributed organizations running on reliable distributed systems. To achieve this vision, we begin with ourselves, adopting a democratic structure that aims to rebalance the power dynamics between capital and labour towards something more sustainable and non-extractive; something that nurtures long term employment and real wealth creation through R&amp;D, entrepreneurship, and innovation; something more like a Zebra than a Unicorn.",
